Direct Known Subclasses:
XDoc
public abstract class Doc
extends java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentLinkedQueue
implements Versioned

Doc is an abstract extension of Queue, that is versioned and removes case restrictions on contains(t) when t is a string. Doc is currently currently serving as a super class for XDoc.

Author:
jhoule
See Also:
XDoc, Serialized Form
